        "text": "Extract invoice data from this document . \nReturn ONLY valid JSON (no markdown, no explanation):\n{\n  \"supplier_company\": \"supplier company name\",\n  \"customer_tax_id\": \"customer Polish Tax-Id (NIP) for QAgile company i.e. 5272928285 or 6171862496\",\n  \"customer_company\": \"company name\",\n  \"invoice_number\": \"invoice number string with numer like 123/12/22\",\n  \"invoice_issued_date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\",\n\"invoice_issued_year\": \"year of issued date in YYYY format i.e. 2025\"\n\"invoice_issued_month-pl\": \"polish name of the issue data month if format MM Monthname i.e. 11 Listopad\",\n  \"invoice_amount_net\": 0.00,\n  \"invoice_amount_tax\": 0.00,\n  \"invoice_amount_gross\": 0.00,\n  \"currency\": \"international format like PLN, USD, EUR\",\n  \"category\": \"short-descriptive-slug\"\n}\n\nCATEGORY SLUG RULES:\n- Use 2-3 words maximum\n- Lowercase, dash-separated (kebab-case)\n- BE SPECIFIC: describe the actual service/product\n- Use English or recognizable brand names\n\nEXAMPLES:\n- Adobe Creative Cloud → \"adobe\"\n- Microsoft Office 365 → \"msoffice\"\n- Fuel/Gas station → \"paliwo\"\n- Car repair Dacia → \"dacia\"\n- Training course → \"szkolenie-agile\" or \"pspo-training\"\n- Medical insurance Medicover → \"medicover\"\n- Mobile Orange → \"orange\"\n- Anthropic API → \"anthropic\"\n- Mailchimp subscription → \"mailchimp\"\n- Office supplies → \"biuro\"\n- Printing services → \"wydruk\"\n- AWS cloud → \"aws\"\n- Car paint/supplies → \"lakier-auto\" or \"farba-volvo\"",
        "inputType": "binary",
        "binaryPropertyName": "=currentFile",
        "options": {}
      },
